{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\lang9\b\fs24 AUDIOBOOKS CHAPTER MARKER \b0: Activating \b0 or \b Arming \b0 this script, by clicking on the point in which a chapter should be added,\line a popup window asks for the chapter title. \par
Writing it and giving \b OK, \b0 a marker will be added with the ID3 TAG "\b CHAP=\b0 " followed by the inserted title.\par
Automatically  a SideCar file is created into the directory of teh project, where the file .RPP is placed.\f1\fs22\par
}

